Package: heatindex
Title: Calculating Heat Stress
Version: 0.0.1
Description: Implements the simpler and faster heat index, which matches the values of the original 1979 heat index and its 2022 extension for air temperatures above 300 K (27 C, 80 F) and with only minor differences at lower temperatures.
URL: https://heatindex.org
